## nova cell delete

Deletes a cell

### Synopsis

Deletes an existing cell.
If no name is given, the default cellname is used (which can be changed with 'nova config set cellname <name>').

```
nova cell delete [name] [flags]
```

```
  -h, --help   help for delete
```
